    <item>
      <title>莱恩表示，欧洲央行需要全年采取限制措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/ecb-will-need-to-be-restrictive-all-year-long-lane-tells-ft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩表示，欧洲央行将于下个月开始降息，但到 2024 年之前都需要维持紧缩政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/ecb-will-need-to-be-restrictive-all-year-long-lane-tells-ft</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 04:17:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
